TEXT.S: mkibuhw i Hualien a kuwan nu Kalinku ku niyazu' nu mkibuhw. u kasalumaluma' nu mkibuhw sa, izaw ku 160 a luma'. kumud nu kasabinawlan sa, izaw ku 450 a tademaw. kasabinawlan nu Ingcumin sa, izaw ku 183 a tademaw, pakalatu 41%. u zuma sa, cay ku Ingcumin, izaw ku 267 a tademaw, pakalatu 59%. u kasabinacadan, 30%, Amis 6%, Tayal 3%, Puyuma 1%.
